cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with analyzing the performance of saliency models and human gaze on degraded images. 
2. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper involves studying human gaze during scene free viewing. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses the effectiveness of data augmentation transformations on deep saliency models. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper involves analyzing the performance of machine learning models (saliency models) on degraded images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing eye movements over images.
